QuestData.Title: Restraining Order
QuestData.Description: "Something feels different"? Dat was all Raal said?$b$bHis flock of pterrordaxes have swarmed de courtyard of Zanchul. Dey are being driven mad.$b$bShoo dem away before dey hurt demselves or others.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Hexlord Raal in Zanchul.
